      • Service

        public Service​(char type,
               java.lang.String ownerId,
               java.lang.String petId,
               Pet clientPet,
               DateIn dateJob)
        Constructor method for class Service which is a service offered by the veterinary.
        Parameters:
        type - The type of service. This param can only be 'b', 'd', 't', 'n' or 's'. It won't get any other char.
        ownerId - The pet's owner ID. This param must not be empty.
        petId - The pet's name. This param must not be empty.
        clientPet - The pet (object). This param must not be null.
        dateJob - The date (object) when the service took place. This param must not be null.
